text: Just reopened, still the same female chef so taste was as good as before! Fish were very fresh and portions were very generous. Prices were reasonable too!
I always eat this in the morning. Love the sweetnesss of the soup and its very clean taste yet cloudy goodness. The fish is also very fresh. Will come again!
Very fresh fish abd seafood at reasonable price. Love their hotpot and thai style sotong. Very yummy. Owner very friendly and good cooj.
